<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:06:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>威尼斯双年展以色列馆馆长表示，我不是以色列的发言人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/im-not-israels-spokeswoman-says-curator-of-israeli-pavilion-at-venice-biennale/0000018e-dce6-dab2-a7ae-ddffbf0c0000</link><description>尽管遭到艺术界的强烈反对以及对亲巴勒斯坦抗议者暴力行为的担忧，威尼斯双年展的以色列馆仍将于本周开放。策展人米拉·拉皮多特 (Mira Lapidot) 对艺术家因其民族身份而受到排斥感到愤怒，同时拒绝将自己视为国家的代表</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:40:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/im-not-israels-spokeswoman-says-curator-of-israeli-pavilion-at-venice-biennale/0000018e-dce6-dab2-a7ae-ddffbf0c0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙停火六周后，哈马斯提议分阶段释放以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hamas-offers-phased-release-of-israeli-hostages-after-six-week-gaza-cease-fire/0000018e-e090-d09b-afff-eebd7b990000</link><description>哈马斯提议分三个阶段释放人质并解除对加沙地带的围困。一名美国高级官员表示，辛瓦尔希望扣留人质，包括年轻妇女、老人和伤员，即使这意味着不会立即停火</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 08:25:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hamas-offers-phased-release-of-israeli-hostages-after-six-week-gaza-cease-fire/0000018e-e090-d09b-afff-eebd7b990000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-黎巴嫩边境附近发生爆炸，四名以色列国防军士兵受伤，其中一人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article-live/u-s-to-explore-measures-to-hold-iran-accountable-at-the-un/0000018e-df82-d4da-a18f-dfa37abc0000</link><description>以色列空军于周一连夜拦截来自东部的无人机 ■ 美国中央司令部称，美军摧毁了 80 架无人机和从伊朗、也门发射的 6 枚导弹 ■ 拜登敦促众议院“尽快”通过援助法案 ■ 后方司令部：教育周一活动照常进行 ■ 法国和英国敦促以色列避免与伊朗的冲突升级</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 02:35:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article-live/u-s-to-explore-measures-to-hold-iran-accountable-at-the-un/0000018e-df82-d4da-a18f-dfa37abc0000</guid></item><item><title>“结盟的机会”或“发狂”：以色列领导人回应伊朗的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/opportunity-for-alliance-or-go-berserk-israels-leaders-respond-to-irans-attack/0000018e-ddf7-d7e5-a1fe-fff794e40000</link><description>随着伊朗袭击以色列事件尘埃落定，以色列政界人士就以色列应如何应对发出了自己的声音。甘茨和加兰特一致认为，这是结盟对抗伊朗的机会，而以色列极右翼领导人则呼吁在德黑兰市中心进行重大报复</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 19:45:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/opportunity-for-alliance-or-go-berserk-israels-leaders-respond-to-irans-attack/0000018e-ddf7-d7e5-a1fe-fff794e40000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗和以色列距离战争还差一个误判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-14/ty-article/.highlight/iran-and-israel-are-still-one-miscalculation-away-from-war/0000018e-dd89-d7e5-a1fe-ffc9a7e40000</link><description>这场噩梦有很多潜在的触发因素。例如，乔丹就处于极其不稳定的境地</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 19:43:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-14/ty-article/.highlight/iran-and-israel-are-still-one-miscalculation-away-from-war/0000018e-dd89-d7e5-a1fe-ffc9a7e40000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击后拜登向以色列传达的信息：趁领先就退出</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/bidens-message-to-israel-after-iran-attack-quit-while-youre-ahead/0000018e-ddc4-d203-a7cf-ffdc8d420000</link><description>在美国竭尽全力帮助以色列成功拦截伊朗的袭击之后，总统现在将目光瞄准了以色列领导人，以避免可能导致该地区全面战争的局势进一步升级，并告诉他们应该抓住这次胜利，并采取行动。继续前行</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 19:00:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/bidens-message-to-israel-after-iran-attack-quit-while-youre-ahead/0000018e-ddc4-d203-a7cf-ffdc8d420000</guid></item><item><title>自杀式无人机、巡航导弹和弹道导弹：伊朗对以色列空袭的详细分析</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/suicide-drones-cruise-and-ballistic-missiles-a-breakdown-of-irans-attack-on-israel/0000018e-dd82-d203-a7cf-ffdee42a0000</link><description>坠落的碎片和照片表明，作为伊朗对以色列领土发动重大袭击的一部分，弹道导弹、GPS制导巡航导弹和带有大型弹头的单向无人机向以色列发射</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 18:17:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/suicide-drones-cruise-and-ballistic-missiles-a-breakdown-of-irans-attack-on-israel/0000018e-dd82-d203-a7cf-ffdee42a0000</guid></item><item><title>幕后花絮：在伊朗大规模袭击期间，美国如何团结起来保卫以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/behind-the-scenes-how-u-s-rallied-to-israels-defense-during-irans-massive-attack/0000018e-dda6-d7e5-a1fe-ffe762960000</link><description>美国官员详细介绍了使用战斗机、军舰、反导系统以及与战略和地区盟友的密切沟通与合作来拦截伊朗对以色列袭击的协调努力</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 17:45:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/behind-the-scenes-how-u-s-rallied-to-israels-defense-during-irans-massive-attack/0000018e-dda6-d7e5-a1fe-ffe762960000</guid></item><item><title>“铁定”支持并呼吁“克制”：全球领导人对伊朗袭击以色列作出反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/global-leaders-send-messages-of-support-to-israel-in-wake-of-irans-major-attack/0000018e-dd5b-deb6-afee-dfdbb79b0000</link><description>在伊朗对以色列发动前所未有的导弹和无人机袭击后，世界上一些最强大国家的领导人向以色列发出了支持和声援的信息。主要阿拉伯领导人发出了更为温和的“担忧”和“克制”信息，俄罗斯将此次袭击视为“自卫”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 16:58:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/global-leaders-send-messages-of-support-to-israel-in-wake-of-irans-major-attack/0000018e-dd5b-deb6-afee-dfdbb79b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 191 天：以色列部长呼吁组建针对伊朗的区域联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-191-israeli-ministers-call-to-form-regional-alliance-against-iran/0000018e-dd4f-deb6-afee-dfdf39fd0000</link><description>伊朗对以色列发动史无前例的袭击，发射了 350 多枚导弹和无人机 ■ 以色列国防军：99% 的发射在美国、英国、法国和约旦的帮助下被拦截 ■ 据报道，拜登警告总理内塔尼亚胡，美国不会参与以色列的任何反制行动攻势 ■ 摩萨德表示，哈马斯拒绝了释放人质/与以色列达成停火协议的最新提议 ■ 战争结束 191 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 16:37:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-191-israeli-ministers-call-to-form-regional-alliance-against-iran/0000018e-dd4f-deb6-afee-dfdf39fd0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登的“不要”信息现在针对以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/bidens-dont-message-is-now-directed-at-israel/0000018e-dcfa-dd58-ad9f-dcff9cef0000</link><description>即使在德黑兰直接袭击之后，对美国来说，防止以色列和伊朗之间的升级仍然是游戏的主题。尽管本杰明·内塔尼亚胡可能希望如此，但华盛顿无意被拖入中东战争</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 15:18:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/bidens-dont-message-is-now-directed-at-israel/0000018e-dcfa-dd58-ad9f-dcff9cef0000</guid></item><item><title>文化综述：为什么以色列女性喜欢拿着枪摆姿势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/cultural-roundup-why-israeli-women-love-posing-with-their-guns/0000018e-dca7-daf5-a7cf-fcbf95dd0000</link><description>一家新书店和文化中心在特拉维夫的时尚中心开业，正当该市居民寻求逃离之际，电视真人秀明星 Maayan Dori 伸手拿枪，年轻女演员诺亚·科恩 (Noa Cohen) 将在同名的圣经传奇故事中扮演玛丽</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 14:44:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/cultural-roundup-why-israeli-women-love-posing-with-their-guns/0000018e-dca7-daf5-a7cf-fcbf95dd0000</guid></item><item><title>学校取消，工作照常：以色列父母在伊朗袭击中争夺托儿服务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/school-day-canceled-work-as-usual-parents-scramble-for-childcare-amid-iranian-attack/0000018e-dc42-dea1-abae-dfeeb8450000</link><description>周六晚上，国内前线司令部宣布，由于即将发生的伊朗空袭，所有教育框架和活动都被取消，而劳动力将照常进行，这让以色列父母陷入了困境。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 12:37:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/school-day-canceled-work-as-usual-parents-scramble-for-childcare-amid-iranian-attack/0000018e-dc42-dea1-abae-dfeeb8450000</guid></item><item><title>贝都因村庄的七岁女孩被伊朗袭击的导弹弹片严重炸伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/seven-year-old-bedouin-girl-critically-injured-by-missile-shrapnel-from-iranian-attack/0000018e-dc3e-dab2-a7ae-ddbf85490000</link><description>阿米娜·哈苏尼 (Amina al-Hassouni) 住在以色列南部一个不为人知的村庄里，头部严重受伤。她的兄弟说，他们被爆炸声吵醒并冲到外面，因为村里没有受保护的避难所</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 11:19:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/seven-year-old-bedouin-girl-critically-injured-by-missile-shrapnel-from-iranian-attack/0000018e-dc3e-dab2-a7ae-ddbf85490000</guid></item><item><title>她的儿子从美国来到以色列军队服役。现在他是人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/her-son-came-from-america-to-serve-in-israels-army-now-hes-a-hostage/0000018e-db90-d01b-abdf-fbffc6010000</link><description>出生于特拉维夫的伊丹·亚历山大 (Edan Alexander) 于 10 月 7 日从军事前哨基地被绑架到加沙。他的母亲希望以色列官员能够像乔·拜登一样提供支持</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 10:42:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/her-son-came-from-america-to-serve-in-israels-army-now-hes-a-hostage/0000018e-db90-d01b-abdf-fbffc6010000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗的袭击对以色列来说是一个战略机遇。内塔尼亚胡会浪费它吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/irans-attack-is-a-strategic-opportunity-for-israel-will-netanyahu-squander-it/0000018e-dbd9-dcf5-a3cf-fbdd980a0000</link><description>周日凌晨发生的史无前例的伊朗袭击事件对以色列及其盟友来说是一个转折点，为以色列提供了真正改变中东局势的可能性，但前提是本杰明·内塔尼亚胡现在采取正确的行动</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 10:18:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/irans-attack-is-a-strategic-opportunity-for-israel-will-netanyahu-squander-it/0000018e-dbd9-dcf5-a3cf-fbdd980a0000</guid></item><item><title>抵御伊朗的袭击是以色列的一项重大成就。报复可能会引发全面地区战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/fending-off-iran-is-a-major-israeli-achievement-retaliation-risks-all-out-war/0000018e-db86-df04-adae-ffd6537f0000</link><description>拜登正在向内塔尼亚胡施压，要求他避免对伊朗进行报复性空袭，并敦促他把重点放在成功拦截无人机和火箭上。 10月7日</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 09:27:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/fending-off-iran-is-a-major-israeli-achievement-retaliation-risks-all-out-war/0000018e-db86-df04-adae-ffd6537f0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：以色列击落伊朗无人机和导弹，向敌人发出“明确信息”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/biden-israel-sent-clear-message-to-its-foes-by-downing-iranian-drones-missiles/0000018e-db3c-ddad-a7ee-fbbd47220000</link><description>拜登在与以色列总理内塔尼亚胡交谈时表示，以色列在防御和击败前所未有的袭击方面“表现出了非凡的能力”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 06:39:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/biden-israel-sent-clear-message-to-its-foes-by-downing-iranian-drones-missiles/0000018e-db3c-ddad-a7ee-fbbd47220000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德称哈马斯拒绝释放人质提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/hamas-rejects-hostage-release-proposal-mossad-says/0000018e-db24-d01b-abdf-fb7ffb470000</link><description>由美国、卡塔尔和埃及斡旋的拟议协议包括释放人质和增加进入加沙的人道主义援助数量</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 06:03:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/hamas-rejects-hostage-release-proposal-mossad-says/0000018e-db24-d01b-abdf-fb7ffb470000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击7小时后以色列领空重新开放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airspace-reopens-after-7-hours-following-iranian-attack/0000018e-db17-d01b-abdf-fb7f3d840000</link><description>特拉维夫本古里安机场的航班时刻表预计将在夜间关闭后发生变化</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 05:41:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airspace-reopens-after-7-hours-following-iranian-attack/0000018e-db17-d01b-abdf-fb7f3d840000</guid></item></channel></rss>